{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":9,"day":5}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"颂歌——长诗“颂歌”第三章","authors":["李瑛"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从我们的党诞生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发黄的线装书上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印着马克思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严峻的嘴里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱着国际歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这一刻起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后便跟踪着——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警察，密探，军犬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后便跟踪着——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜捕，屠杀，恫吓……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数次斗争，无数次失败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年又一年艰辛的岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一片暗礁累累的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而在我们自己的队伍里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能来领航、掌舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能战胜万里风波？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么时候，什么时候呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你才能驶入航道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开那些礁滩、漩涡？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，一个巨人——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他从先进的革命青年群中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从工厂阴暗的车间里出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，又在湖南农村的街道上行走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他敲过多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农家的窗棂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在昏黄的灯光下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考虑，分析，思索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用马克思列宁主义的显微镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观察时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"研究敌我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎能想象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张小小的桌面上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却审慎地解剖着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个历史，整个阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个村庄，整个中国……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的文献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不朽的著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人们上了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样伟大的一课！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我们的党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然多么幼稚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍在风雨中口颠簸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还拉不稳革命的缆索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军阀的指挥刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主的皮鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野蛮的屠刀下烈士的鲜血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在五十岁的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了那黑夜将尽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲晓的天色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时，严峻的历史呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在拷问每个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要每个人作出抉择："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是跪着活？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是站着活？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但从工厂主的皮鞭下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑出的苦力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从地主的后院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃出的长工以及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"觉醒的起义的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在扬着尘土的大道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆炸起不屈的歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“起来，饥寒交迫的奴隶……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸腾的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲撞着沉睡的中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知道已经多少次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人无尽的叫嚣和咒骂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了对付共产党人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们筑一座监狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一座监狱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打一副镣锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一副镣锁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们梦想一个早晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能把共产党人杀光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是仇恨哺育的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的人民，早变得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比铁还坚强得多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比钢还坚强得多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山哨口的篝火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃起全国人民最大的希望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾的溪涧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啸着全国人民最高的歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东同志率红军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到你的胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从山巅俯瞰动荡的山河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩大红军，争取群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建立根据地，实行土地改革。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是一双草鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏遍多少大小山河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片片苏区象绿洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散落在大戈壁似的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干旱的中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样斗争？怎样胜利？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又以他不朽的学说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阐述了英明的策略："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“星星之火，可以燎原”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是号召，是理论的答复，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准确的估价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英明的预见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人民巨大的鼓舞和鞭策。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那历史的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雷雨的暗夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们保存、发展和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮大了自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建立了自己的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农民主共和国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵，星罗棋布的老苏区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗猎猎卷战歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥磨梭镖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹系红缨——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤卫队员的臂章如火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照彻万里山河……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那最艰苦的岁月里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们望着你，谁都相信："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天去武装我们的农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天就夺回全部的城郭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，呵！我的祖国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派出精锐的师旅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又请来英国顾问，德国参谋……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那远涉重洋运来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮，摩托，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾压塌多少茅屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震灭多少摇颤的灯火……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次——十万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二次——二十万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三次——三十万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四次——五十万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五次——一百万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“追截”，“围剿”，“扫荡”，“封锁”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次比一次更残酷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次比一次更凶恶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰辛的岁月会证明："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，资产阶级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早昏倒在沙发上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小资产阶级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有人在院里慌张"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收拾箱笼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这严重的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义又一次闯进了中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸血的大地永远会记得："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五岭山头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泸定铁索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那罕无人烟的雪山草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二万五千里呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篝火曾燃起多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高昂的歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让长征向世界宣告吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义、反动派"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扼杀不了我们红军好汉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让长征向祖国呼唤吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来，不屈的奴隶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从马克思列宁主义去寻找你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天的生活！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让长征这巨大的播种机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下满地倔强的种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚信呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，明天就会是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花万朵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我千歌万颂属于你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一座都市和村落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我却更爱万山环绕的遵义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九三五年一月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，开始实现了你英明的策略"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——党的伟大的转折呵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们欢呼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们找到了自己英明的舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远跟着他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远航跋涉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，毛主席从这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带领我们走到新中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土延安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓缓流荡的延河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫八年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果说中国在战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那即是说——你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在西北高原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威严挺立，高昂着头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你领导千百万群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成统一战线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面抗击日本鬼子和汉奸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面揭露国民党的阴谋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在解放区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在敌后根据地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江南北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河滩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈！为保卫我们的民族和土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国掀起了冲天的恕吼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听！座座山头在呼唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条道路在嘱托："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决不做亡国奴呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上前线！打鬼子！救中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是多少村口呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子送亲人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少灯下呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲动刀尺；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少等待，多少焦灼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声枪响，飞来多少传说……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们的每寸土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为战斗曾献出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么巨大的爱情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每秒钟曾怎样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在艰辛中度过！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年，整整八年呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你以你的大谋略、大机智，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导着人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双肩挑起民族危亡的重担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀和油印号外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记载着我们浴血的生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，终于响彻了战斗的凯歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间已经多少次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考验了反动派和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大资产阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至死也改变不了他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狐狸般狡诈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼般贪婪的性格。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席早看穿了他的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一根神经，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是多少次告诉我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们曾有过多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“自由”、“民主”的许诺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能相信他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“善心”的施舍！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以人民的意志战斗呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以革命的名义战斗呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到大反攻的军号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹红了雕敝的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄上空的朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂晓传来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追击的马蹄得得……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是时候了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该以主人的身份，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清点自己残破的山河："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月——千里滚沸的辽河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月——淮海的红旗如火！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更难忘那严峻的早晨——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天津的硝烟，北京的凯歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几场伟大的战略决战呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使国内外一切敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞魂散魄……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但那戴着肩章丝穗的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并没有认识我们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是毛主席一声命令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直下中原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光中数不清的捷报纷飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月夜长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩荡荡的万膛竞射。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南下呵，南下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排山倒海的兵马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接天盖地的粮秣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回来，南京！回来，祖国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回来，我们失去千年的欢乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩断他野藤一样盘络的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四大家族的根须；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈碎他金镶银镂的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总统登基的宝座；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那沉沉暗夜的时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已如一张薄纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎抵得住党的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一五○口径的重炮齐射！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“将革命进行到底”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席又向我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出了庄严的号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“将革命进行到底”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七个大字呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推动了数百万大军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤亿万人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摧枯拉朽，山呼海啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲刷着腐朽的中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气势惊天地呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮志撼山河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗啦啦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹动了历史的篇页。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始了怎样伟大的转折！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，一个秋天的早晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们追击到国境线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勒住马嚼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一缕清风，忽然送来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席庄严的宣告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国人民站起来了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句话，催开多少鲜花朵朵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这一刻呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千年的云霾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐化作万里似锦的云霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五亿人的心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐涌现欢乐的大波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能记载你的功绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"史诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能记录你的荣耀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看中国的大地呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听不绝的爆竹锣鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不尽的旗帜狂歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这一刻呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不想起五千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流着兴奋的眼泪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这一刻呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不想起我自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去、未来一生的长河；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不想起周围的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志、亲人和朋友！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我更怎能不想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英明的领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你领导我们推倒我们头上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三座大山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有多少话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向你倾诉，要向你说；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我说呵，说呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又说些什么！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但此时，毛主席又"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长征只是迈出第一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面还有更多的险山恶水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待我们攀援、跋涉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可又有什么能阻止我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰骋的骏马——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风万里下江河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前人没想过的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们想了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前人没做过的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要做。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用竞赛的口号和欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充实每一个劳动日；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用花的颜色，草的颜色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点染每一天每一刻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看吧，让全世界看吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们九百多万平方公里的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子将腾起多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的神话和传说！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}